{"tid":920921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巨乳婚攝師現場與男賓做愛 還到樹邊尿尿及咒罵新人家族","createTime":"2018-11-29T07:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T11:11:33.000Z","uid":72009,"like":103,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"90361e0052e9015e784c3b2f4db1a66e78880562","tid":920921,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"美國一名婚禮攝影師梅塔(Katherine Leigh Mehta)在上周六的一場婚禮上，進行攝影工作，但她卻與一名男賓客直接在空房間裡做愛，還到戶外場地的樹邊放尿，更大聲咒罵新人家族，要他們去死，最後梅塔被警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，梅塔於周六在德州一處婚宴場擔任婚攝工作，但在現場一名保全接獲通報，發現梅塔在一個房間裡，正在和一名男賓客做愛。保全當場把梅塔請出去，但梅塔卻跌跌撞撞地走到戶外場地噴水池，開始大叫咒罵：「你們全家人都在聖誕節之前死一死，你們所有的女兒都會死，你們都會死，去死吧！」梅塔甚至靠近一棵樹，當場放尿。<br />\n<br />\n之後家屬報警處理，梅塔也隨即被警方逮捕，周日獲得保釋，警方認為事發當時，梅塔有飲酒並混藥物吞下。但梅塔的父親不相信女兒會出現這種行為，她的姊妹更是為她辯解：「她當時在不知情的狀況下喝下烈酒，之後她跑去外面，更發現有兩名怪怪的男生要靠近她，準備對她做出不利的事，於是她大叫，企圖尋求支援，但最後整個情勢反轉，所有狀況都對對梅塔不利。」<br />\n<br />\n另外報導指出，梅塔除了是婚攝師，平時也兼差當泳衣模特兒，以「Max McIntyre」藝名上傳影片到YouTube。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181129/640_6e32ad20c479cbca8b86c97d36c12155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181129%2F640_6e32ad20c479cbca8b86c97d36c12155.jpg&h=13c449b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181129/640_444b2e40ba19ff7dcbf96e5aa41fa94b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181129%2F640_444b2e40ba19ff7dcbf96e5aa41fa94b.jpg&h=ce1d0087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181129/640_ed3aa87d88c471814677bece280249b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181129%2F640_ed3aa87d88c471814677bece280249b4.jpg&h=2183d329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82176b8916082cf09cba0530514190f289cf4111","tid":920921,"uid":11055,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:45:57.000Z","msg":"當我有講過"},{"pid":"b8b6b66a93dfc9487d96a5222bcc7b90c4660ff8","tid":920921,"uid":115801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"即刻上youtube search 「Max McIntyre」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uE5hjEDts9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuE5hjEDts9Q&d=WoLvZM8B45wHJ3cTJ3oPmMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5a65fafc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uE5hjEDts9Q</a>"},{"pid":"c7a261dfb2be0f8695f66d73fd8afd2d99bc89e5","tid":920921,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"好！想！屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab855214685b481e505a302d12b8158832bc3ffc","tid":920921,"uid":172914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"我一定有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256fa6fe9e60016c82c894fc5f7a92b814f0f332","tid":920921,"uid":55659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f9917ee75e31e0d6cd7b4defe7b99169255a35","tid":920921,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img